"""
Tests for organization API endpoints.

Tests the org CRUD and membership management endpoints,
including bulk member operations.

Test-data setup uses the composable factories declared in
``tests/conftest.py`` (``user_factory``, ``org_factory``,
``owner_with_org``). Anywhere the literal email/slug value isn't the
test's point, prefer the factory; otherwise inline with a one-line
comment naming the invariant.
"""
